OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning very
OL,6,Fwindy, with inland gales, perhaps
OL,7,Fsevere over hills. Blustery rain and
OL,8,Fshowers quickly moving through before
OL,9,Fmidnight. Turning drier and colder,
OL,10,Fwith winds easing through the early
OL,11,Fhours of Monday, but perhaps the odd
OL,12,Fshower still possible.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FBright and breezy Easter
OL,15,FSunday with some sunny spells to
OL,16,Fstart. Cloud then thickening, with
OL,17,Fblustery showers during the afternoon,
OL,18,Fbefore late sunny spells follow.
OL,19,FFeeling cooler than Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
