OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbut cloudy Monday. Staying fine with
OL,7,Fwarm sunshine Tuesday, but cooler in
OL,8,Fany onshore breeze. Chilly starts,
OL,9,Fwith perhaps some frost. Very warm
OL,10,Fsunshine Wednesday, before cloud
OL,11,Fthickens later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
